<?-
  Mutation Test: Nested While Loops (10 levels)
  Tests compiler/parser handling of while loop nesting at maximum allowed depth.

  Complexity: 1 (base) + 10 (while loops) + 10 (comparisons) = 21 (under 50 limit)
  Nesting depth: 10 (at maximum limit)
